flowchart TD
  A[Visitor opens sign-up page] --> B{Platform requires invitation?}
  B -- Yes, no invitation --> C[Show invitation code prompt]
  B -- No or valid invitation --> D[Render registration form]
  D --> E[Show required registration agreements]
  E --> F[Visitor opens agreement modal]
  F --> G[Turbo frame loads seeded agreement page]
  G --> H{Scrolled through full agreement?}
  H -- No --> I[Checkbox remains locked]
  H -- Yes --> J[Stimulus unlocks matching checkbox]
  J --> K[Visitor checks all required agreements]
  K --> L[Submit registration form]
  L --> M{All required agreements accepted?}
  M -- No --> N[Render validation errors]
  M -- Yes --> O[Create user and agreement participant records]
  O --> P[Registration completes]
